The paper focuses on a task of leveraging reviews to build an agent that can answer multi-turn questions from potential consumers of online businesses. This task involves natural language processing, information retrieval, machine learning, and potentially cybersecurity (to ensure the safety of online businesses). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
